{"tid":2362166,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內媒罕有低調 新華社斥「歹毒」","createTime":"2021-01-11T09:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T09:51:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45b96f356493400b7ef41d25b15bcea537e6d850","tid":2362166,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/KX5F5PXOSVDQPI7QM3YA6RVLOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2FKX5F5PXOSVDQPI7QM3YA6RVLOY%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BTw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=085b5945\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2FKX5F5PXOSVDQPI7QM3YA6RVLOY%2F&h=dc2bf174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/KX5F5PXOSVDQPI7QM3YA6RVLOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內媒罕有低調 新華社斥「歹毒」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/02KhzNZShs7hcAUopJVhY7q9BRI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HEZYT5CXW5CIVNKYZOI4L57JZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F02KhzNZShs7hcAUopJVhY7q9BRI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHEZYT5CXW5CIVNKYZOI4L57JZA.jpg&h=9a6665bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國拒再迎合北京，容許台灣官員訪美。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧宣佈撤銷美台官員的交往限制後，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美台撤外交限制 蔡英文可訪白宮 《環時》：向世界和平扔原子彈<br />\n<br />\n昨日發表的新華國際時評，批評美國少數政客只顧個人政治利益，「掄起大錘一通亂砸」，不惜砸壞中美關係，給繼任者留下爛攤子。時評認為，政客在台灣問題上不擇手段，無非是想轉移矛盾，最後撈點「翻本籌碼」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台反擊︰堅定捍衞主權<br />\n<br />\n《環時》評論的言辭則更為激烈，形容這是對兩岸和平、中美關係保持底線穩定的有犯罪性質的結構性破壞，又稱要警告台灣，「如果他們跟着喪心病狂，美國現政府的最後幾天，也有可能是台灣民進黨政權存在的最後幾天」。台陸委會稱留意到《環時》偏激言論，將持續堅定捍衞主權與民主，反對非理性、非和平的作為與言論。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拜登倘推翻如向中共示弱<br />\n<br />\n《環時》引述分析稱，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由於內地主流傳媒一片低調，社交平台對事件的討論次數亦較少。部份網民稱不怕開戰，可以乘機武統台灣。「丟掉幻想，准備戰鬥，才是上策！」。<br />\n<br />\n微博/新華社"},{"pid":"b2b54c2509c1291449756ad0ef6d606c6aa38fd9","tid":2362166,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"講毒邊夠中國黎<br />\n成日話人歹毒<br />\n又唔望下自己國家d空氣同野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a219df841c432bcb1e400451d565ee95e3340c","tid":2362166,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b54c2509c1291449756ad0ef6d606c6aa38fd9","tid":2362166,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"講毒邊夠中國黎<br />\n成日話人歹毒<br />\n又唔望下自己國家d空氣同野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"呢一期咁鍾意用「歹毒」呢個字眼既？搞到連比家超都「歹毒」一番。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}